{
  "stem": "393.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it was a terrible time over there already, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Besides our own private sufferings, you see, there were already-- there were very, very strict laws.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was the Judenrat-- I don't know if you know about that-- who-- who were the right hand of the Nazis, because the Jewish had to ask the Jews for money, jewelry, everything, everything.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they started the deported-- it was while I was there they gathered, already, the young girls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took them to the concentration camp, which I didn't know that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They thought they-- we are taken to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As I-- as I mentioned, I was spared because I was a foreigner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't think they knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think people knew that they are going, some of them, to their death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in Auschwitz already, when I couldn't believe it, what's happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- It was the last, last time before the tragedy over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we found out, over there, that there is a group of people, who are from Hungary, who are going to the borders.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to that group, to see their [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me that they got a so-called [NON-ENGLISH]-- passport-- from the Germans, that they are strangers here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They belong to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they can go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Germans gave them [GERMAN]-- that's how it's called in Germany-- to get to the Hungarian borders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we attached ourselves to that group, and went with them, from town to town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have too much packages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And sometimes the Jewish congregation-- whatever, the Jewish what is it-- they gave us a wagon so we should-- [INAUDIBLE] sometimes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It depended.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
